deploy-job:
    stage: deploy
    script:
        - echo "deploy job started"
        - sleep 10s
        - echo "deploy job completed"

Note : in order to execute the jobs in order stages needs to be defined , based on the successfull completion of the stage next job will be executed else other jobs will be skipped.
